          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SITA",
                "EXTB",
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Energy-Loss Corrections were Applied to Determine the",
                "Energy Halfway Through the Targets According to",
                "C.F. Williamson Et Al., Cea-R3042 (1966).  To Reduce",
                "Background, in Case of Gamma-Measurements the Targets",
                "Were Transferred by Means of a Pneumatic Shuttle",
                "Between Irradiation Position and a Low Background",
                "Counting Area Within About 0.3 Sec.  For Proton",
                "Measurements, the Si-Detector was Pulled Back 2.3 Cm",
                "During the Irradiation Periods. Four Successive",
                "Spectra were Recorded in Multi-Spectrum Scaling Mode."
              ]
            }
          ],
